Text: thank you so much, I love this comic

I would really, really appreciate it if you could seed for a little bit - I've loved this comic since I was like 15; even have about the first 12-15 issues signed&sketched by Mark (he had a lot more time back then lol)

I promise to buy the whole series; I'm just not in Canada anymore... any chance of getting the new volume, "The Winter Book"?

THANKS A MILLION!
